Class VariableConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.rdg.resc.edal.catalogue.jaxb.VariableConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EnhancedVariableMetadata

    public class VariableConfig
extends Object
implements EnhancedVariableMetadata
    A class representing a variable in the XML config. This contains all of the information needed to define the EnhancedVariableMetadata which contains default plotting options etc.
    Author:
    Guy Griffiths
